### Problem description

when trying to generate types from a proto file for example

```proto
syntax = "proto3";

package echo.service;


service EchoService {
  rpc echo (Hello) returns (Replay) {}
}

message Hello {
  string name = 1;
}

message Replay {
    string message = 1;
}
```

it generates an optional type for the request but not for the handler

```typescript
export interface Hello {
  name?: string;
}

export interface Hello__Output {
  name: string;
}
```

I would expect a strict type for both types since `optional` modifier is not used in the proto file

